                                                                    java.lang.String labelCode)
Gets the attributes associated with a given label for a given type.

Parameters:
discrValue - the discrimnator value of the type: structure code of a key flexfield or context value of a descriptive flexfield
labelCode - the code of the label
Returns:
the list of attributes associated with the label; an empty list if no attributes are associated with the given label
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if no view definition is found for the given discriminator value
FlexfieldJboException - if the properties used to store the label information are corrupted
